---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Privacy Policy | Net Worth Calculator by Age" description="Privacy policy for NetWorthCalc. 100% client-side calculation guarantee with zero data collection.">
	<main class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 py-12 md:py-20">
		<header class="text-center mb-12">
			<h1 class="text-4xl font-bold text-white mb-4">Privacy Policy</h1>
			<p class="text-slate-400">Last updated: {new Date().toLocaleDateString('en-US', { month: 'long', day: 'numeric', year: 'numeric' })}</p>
		</header>

		<div class="glass-panel p-8 md:p-12 rounded-3xl border border-white/10 bg-slate-900/60 backdrop-blur-xl text-slate-300 space-y-6">
			<section>
				<h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-white mb-2">1. 100% Client-Side Calculations</h2>
				<p>Your privacy is paramount. NetWorthCalc executes all age, income, and net worth percentile calculations locally in your Web browser. We do not store, record, or transmit your financial inputs to any server.</p>
			</section>

			<section>
				<h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-white mb-2">2. Cookies and Local Storage</h2>
				<p>We do not use tracking cookies to build personal user profiles. Local storage may be utilized solely to remember your preferred age or currency preferences across browser visits.</p>
			</section>

			<section>
				<h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-white mb-2">3. Advertising Networks</h2>
				<p>We may display non-intrusive advertisements served by networks like Google AdSense or Mediavine. These partners may use anonymized cookies to deliver relevant ad content according to their privacy policies.</p>
			</section>
		</div>
	</main>
</Layout>
